WEBVTT

00:03:57.276 --> 00:04:00.065
supply is in steady decline.

00:04:01.728 --> 00:04:03.410
To put things in perspective,

00:04:03.434 --> 00:04:08.498
half of the students
completing high school today in Australia

00:04:08.522 --> 00:04:11.196
are not prepared
to understand any argument

00:04:11.220 --> 00:04:13.220
about rates of change in data.

00:04:14.363 --> 00:04:16.053
In this digital age

00:04:16.077 --> 00:04:19.990
where fake news can influence
election results,

00:04:20.014 --> 00:04:22.482
this is very concerning.

00:04:23.458 --> 00:04:25.149
Let me give you a concrete example.

00:04:25.173 --> 00:04:27.172
Let's take a closer look at that graph.

00:04:27.673 --> 00:04:30.712
Can everyone see what I've done there
to stress my point?